---
title: Cozy Chicken Pot Pie & Biscuits Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: This homey customizable chicken pot pie bar will delight the whole table! In a quick 35 minutes, you’ll set out chicken pot pie filling packed with dark meat chicken and potatoes in a creamy sauce, plus warm, flaky biscuits brushed with garlic-herb butter. Pair that with sweet roasted carrots and lemony green beans for everyone to build their own perfect plate. Order mushrooms and/or broccoli for extra veggies on the table.

